{"title":"Caidas Adulto Mayor NICE2025-1","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Geriatría/Caidas Adulto Mayor NICE2025-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Caídas en el\\NAdulto Mayor","guid":"5ecMcQUhSWq5w6nlX0moIA","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Definición y\\NConcepto","guid":"uB9drmnTRy6yAluMnGdbTQ","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Evento inadvertido con desplazamiento al suelo o nivel inferior","guid":"Lb_J-OIwSR-gbyJwN8x1Mw","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"SIN pérdida de conciencia previa NI pérdida de tono postural","guid":"lgralmCJT8W7OGBbyrY8qg","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"SÍNDROME GERIÁTRICO → no diagnóstico aislado → síntoma de condición de base","guid":"m9CQYFWeQaO-vyiEcTGssQ","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"No es evento normal del envejecimiento → signo de fragilidad o patología","guid":"bVtqxJodS82TZzZVooqJYQ","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"Síncope puede simular caída si hay amnesia retrógrada","guid":"L8phrEY4T7iU2JY87SpYOQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"aFlEFmrHS4-P6BZ8zaei_Q","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"Comunidad","guid":"dCM5jyuORfSjAfwt2aLleQ","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"1/3 de >65a caen en 1 año","guid":"9MagQtazQ1yxhN4akgURGA","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"8","text":"40% de >80a caen al menos 1 vez/año","guid":"OGL40NghQO64rYow9ZqX9Q","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"8","text":"60% de los que caen 1 vez → vuelven a caer","guid":"p_xUe86JQ2ySYG09IQ0CYg","children":[]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"7","text":"Institucionalizados","guid":"4xzRlYcNSUmVXhgJjNKC8A","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"50% caen anualmente (rango 30-56%)","guid":"Qyh5Cb0eSW6ZE-xWqpMaPQ","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"12","text":"21% caen el PRIMER MES de ingreso → vigilancia extrema","guid":"RxDX43I6TEShQjDVuGF4ZQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"7","text":"Hospitalizados","guid":"KGmaSNLqQp-YtqRgCv8LMw","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"2% en sala general","guid":"lzY1h2qRSN-xhdTXr4puYw","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"15","text":"27% en UGA","guid":"V6eLNDQ3RTeeYhHrRyNUiw","children":[]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"7","text":"Mayoría ocurren de día → solo 20% entre 21:00-07:00","guid":"-y4iuwOkTnKTerYotCNexQ","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"7","text":"Caídas <2m → mecanismo común de trauma mayor en AM","guid":"aQKdPaueTB-oSjxUPjcq8w","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"7","text":"PRIMERA causa de fractura de cadera (95%)","guid":"bxbuzpzxRueGOzACga7mNQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"0","text":"Mecanismo de\\NCaída y Fracturas","guid":"d2zmb4D-REq7U4Aj9ufuOw","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"Anteroposterior → fractura de muñeca (65-75a)","guid":"CRJ6VrlZRZqdNGeUpzgCkw","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"21","text":"Lateral → fractura de cadera (>75a)","guid":"1h9R7OFITFSt18JOZlAWeg","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"Pérdida del reflejo de paracaídas → cambio patrón muñeca a cadera","guid":"d70xFIasSwqmfetUmAjAQA","children":[]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"21","text":"Posterior → poco relacionado con fracturas","guid":"ASa6z2xNQpuJPuHsnd_ZSA","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"21","text":"Síncopes → 2-10% de las causas de caídas","guid":"EK9lzPz1S1KVL0NBaOfi9Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"0","text":"Fisiología de\\NMarcha y\\NEquilibrio","guid":"tTKfYkJKQqe51Syi6K0quQ","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"Sistemas\\Nimplicados","guid":"B5qHyQaZTSC15FwUYyQUbw","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"Aferente (sensorial) → visual + vestibular + propioceptivo","guid":"M9cYxmELQ4mwwA5DWZhhuw","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"28","text":"SNC → corteza frontal (planificación) + ganglios basales (dopamina) + cerebelo + tronco + médula","guid":"tAIGvg4vSOmgyO9acOEQ1Q","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"28","text":"Efector → CV, huesos, articulaciones, pies","guid":"3yuAcDDzTWCuRjJ_mVZGPg","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"28","text":"Cognitivo → atención y función ejecutiva influyen directamente","guid":"D01j1qzyQkG0J-ZpGrz6Kg","children":[]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"27","text":"Estrategias\\Nposturales","guid":"ro9ax4j0R6KCDrbwmQB4tQ","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"Estrategia de tobillo (perturbaciones pequeñas)","guid":"QF3AsL2ETtGVTw5dZkybBg","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"Estrategia de cadera (perturbaciones mayores)","guid":"IaE3MTEXQByI0q8E_cwehQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"36","parent":"27","text":"Cambios con\\Nenvejecimiento","guid":"mTI7KeC8T9O9_T_lqUdnjA","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"Velocidad marcha estable hasta 70a → luego -15%/década marcha común, -20% marcha rápida","guid":"hHRv5VD-TmymkrIiAESSvw","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"Pasos más cortos al mismo ritmo (debilidad pantorrilla)","guid":"wjT9Rn8JTaqlbbStoIhh0Q","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"36","text":"Tiempo doble apoyo → jóvenes 18% vs AM >26%","guid":"2Km2HIKYS7a3raEJXqf2VA","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"36","text":"Cifosis dorsal desplaza centro gravedad anterior","guid":"udBY6Tq-RCqw9-1r7JJLhQ","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"36","text":"Menor flexión plantar y extensión rodilla","guid":"0BkW58RySy23URxCDezAIA","children":[]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"27","text":"Marcha senil → CONTROVERSIA → alteraciones son marcadores precoces de patología (demencia)","guid":"mswuoG2BR-yuuYAFVx1diw","children":[]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"0","text":"Factores\\Nde Riesgo","guid":"7jpy-oazRO-m3KPMQtOsNQ","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"Intrínsecos","guid":"4NTBwF3tQ0iCBhmip2MEcg","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"DEBILIDAD MUSCULAR → RR/OR 4.9 (1.9-10.3) → PRINCIPAL","guid":"AFm6dIGARM-Xb0X_xFboWg","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"44","text":"Déficit de balance → OR 3.2 (1.6-5.4)","guid":"pD3H8ZQrSYe-tQ5nGsLCRQ","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"44","text":"Déficit de marcha → OR 3.0 (1.7-4.8)","guid":"kzdEL-CxRNG3mCdHkBwpLg","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"44","text":"Déficit visual → OR 2.8 (1.1-7.4)","guid":"TZkF0XGcQ2iuMOYeEj1_Tg","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"Contraste y profundidad > agudeza visual pura","guid":"U9KXnv8QTUGpTYuaX0zcGw","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"44","text":"Limitación movilidad → OR 2.5 (1.0-5.3)","guid":"ZZYShqBjQyOZ-8Dls-Zi6A","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"44","text":"Deterioro cognitivo\\N→ OR 2.4 (2.0-4.7)","guid":"Zby-SOPFT0a8I4_HM4qEHw","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"Riesgo +20% por cada punto menos en MMSE","guid":"oTL-FPQHQNWH96vhwKETPg","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"51","text":"DCL NO amnésico (frontal/ejecutivo) → caen MÁS que Alzheimer típico","guid":"Dj8MKgCHTv-wbcy_pka9cg","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"44","text":"Estado funcional alterado → OR 2.0 (1.0-3.1)","guid":"AhD6AMmFRcO23qKadafXKw","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"44","text":"Hipotensión ortostática\\N→ OR 1.9 (1.0-3.4)","guid":"YylDme0JRTKBXRbNYdLRZA","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"30% en >65a, 70% institucionalizados","guid":"3iTio7HFQUuctuvOxPFWhQ","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"55","text":"Hipotensión postprandial → caída PAS >=20mmHg 2h post comida","guid":"VGMl3_aQRguAFoB1j9MKJg","children":[]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"44","text":"Edad → riesgo lesión seria 4x mayor en >85a vs 65-74a","guid":"b43sDKKeR4eSbyjxdtPehg","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"44","text":"Sexo femenino → base marcha estrecha, osteoporosis, sarcopenia","guid":"WP-f1nQ4QHqpZ8wHSOf1TA","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"44","text":"Caídas previas → predictor potente → 2da caída tiene mayor mortalidad","guid":"zivmuMd_Tlm_7_SiPc58CA","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"44","text":"Vitamina D <10 → mayor pérdida masa muscular; <20 → peor performance","guid":"OO78ez0zSq-SYXRtfkjXRQ","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"44","text":"Diabetes → neuropatía + visión + cognición; insulina RR 2.76","guid":"8mtz0lDzTh6PPMFFFdx7Kw","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"44","text":"Parkinson → rigidez, bradicinesia","guid":"lU2dbzsxTAaK9Er9w3T-7g","children":[]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"43","text":"Extrínsecos\\N(ambientales)","guid":"KCzC2Ac9Sd-gUQJU9YCUwg","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"Calzado inadecuado → zapatillas, calcetines, descalzo, taco >2.5cm","guid":"LAoECD23SD-WOtcFU8M9Qg","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"Domicilio → baño, alfombras, iluminación → bajar escaleras > subir","guid":"zU6n5nQ4QSaDRDscsNpaKg","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"64","text":"Institucionalización → FR en sí mismo","guid":"yHNgH0gWRsWx3rhyvTHiUg","children":[]}]},{"id":"68","parent":"43","text":"Precipitantes\\N(estresores agudos)","guid":"dbVUrMS4Q5K4p0kvBwT83w","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"Resbalones, tropiezos","guid":"a1jGCPdfRoaIceN5g8V0Zw","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"68","text":"Síncope, mareo agudo, convulsión","guid":"_lofuLQAQNaoBluM8XX0ww","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"68","text":"Inicio o ajuste farmacológico → MAYOR riesgo primeras 24h","guid":"9SRk9N_cSheWp_RWQgqd4g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"0","text":"Fármacos y\\NCaídas","guid":"UrRbPctkSVeV8oELiQ2EQg","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"PRINCIPAL factor de riesgo MODIFICABLE","guid":"pus4oO7tTK66L8Vm3zuZUg","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"Psicofármacos →\\Naumentan riesgo hasta 40%","guid":"7KseBA_4RkeIbGCsUh-DTA","children":[{"id":"75","parent":"74","text":"Antidepresivos → OR 1.68 (1.47-1.91); ATC > ISRS > Trazodona","guid":"JE0R7a8BTmK7z2u9wbPLdA","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"74","text":"Antipsicóticos → OR 1.59 (1.37-1.83)","guid":"-Km-vR7xQJCtVD5Tf2wc9Q","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"74","text":"Hipnóticos/sedantes → OR 1.47 (1.35-1.62)","guid":"LiQtvQW7R5KR5yAOg0eqbA","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"74","text":"Benzodiazepinas → OR 1.57 (1.43-1.72)","guid":"UAn5C2-ZTS2Y2JqienQgDg","children":[]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"72","text":"Cardiovasculares","guid":"LSQt7DVGSiqG2qTn1lz7iw","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"Antihipertensivos → OR 1.24 (1.01-1.50)","guid":"1a4ryvTJS_WUgojvIZIVcg","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"Digoxina → OR 1.59","guid":"OOkq4-RETcWz4oCBehNi9A","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"79","text":"Diuréticos → OR 1.07 (urgencia miccional + deshidratación)","guid":"4IezC5JJTa-2iPX9dIxGjg","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"79","text":"Betabloqueadores → NO significativa","guid":"XO5SCxuHRW6Wqwjfw-_99Q","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"79","text":"Vasodilatadores → mayor riesgo","guid":"ZTsQX8qVRIKxVsb00gi34Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"72","text":"Antiepilépticos → OR 1.75 (sedación, ataxia)","guid":"RQCPKu7uTmSPlVtzI4aV5Q","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"72","text":"Insulina → RR 2.76; hipoglicemiantes orales sin mayor riesgo","guid":"J-Q4VKItQU-WevXA-F0p-g","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"72","text":"AINEs → OR 1.21 (1.01-1.44)","guid":"7AguUZ6OQKuZQAyiwGEmkA","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"72","text":"Bloqueadores alfa (tamsulosina) → riesgo aumentado","guid":"s3sEUAcZRKW7ySdZIJKukQ","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"72","text":"Narcóticos → NO asociación clara","guid":"byVCGthkQ2SIXIbzdmPShg","children":[]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"0","text":"Osteosarcopenia","guid":"33SD-HgYTzaMeyMn1qoatg","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"Comunicación bioquímica y mecánica músculo-hueso","guid":"iUDoWI2iT_qcxVK1jv85NA","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"90","text":"Sarcopénicos → caen MÁS que osteoporóticos","guid":"jlPYMXeRQ4moKac7ehRR2w","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"90","text":"Osteoporóticos → se fracturan más pero caen menos","guid":"_kS8q5u_TMOspAX--btD2A","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"90","text":"OSTEOSARCOPÉNICOS → PEORES outcomes (caen + se fracturan)","guid":"BjzLFU58SA-rgJIG4Plwaw","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"90","