6","text":"Oportunista → controles, exámenes periódicos","guid":"hmXP12bXT7SnzDOHRwuT0Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"129","parent":"121","text":"Criterios para evaluación INTEGRAL\\N(si caída en último año)","guid":"xLo4iAUHQRSEqY6WbnANPA","children":[{"id":"130","parent":"129","text":">=2 caídas en 12 meses","guid":"02c3Ig3FS3GMHsqRfMjYkA","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"129","text":"Viviendo con fragilidad","guid":"XjjJPbOMTiGRcnPcecMZ3g","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"129","text":"Pérdida de conciencia asociada","guid":"fZ5V5MNYQ2iF0i27U_tReg","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"129","text":"Lesión que requirió tratamiento","guid":"Fr5VXSnoSCSBckTP_E3nTA","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"129","text":"Incapacidad de levantarse solo","guid":"ybNaANxoTJuxYjdk8Di_UQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"135","parent":"121","text":"Si 1 caída SIN criterios anteriores\\N→ evaluar marcha y balance","guid":"w5hNjTNDRxm5xMk0-ctRmA","children":[{"id":"136","parent":"135","text":"Alteración → programa ejercicio + evaluación hogar","guid":"cl8kAJ7ySjODlt02bmNFTQ","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"135","text":"Normal → información y consejo actividad física","guid":"nJ8dUGiBSMa8OOe3NQNowQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"138","parent":"121","text":"Hospitalizados y residencias → evaluación integral AUTOMÁTICA","guid":"I73rXy49SD-1Sr4rAjDveQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"139","parent":"0","text":"Evaluación Integral\\Nde Caídas","guid":"G0qDKxIYQdGgtScfqwHv2g","children":[{"id":"140","parent":"139","text":"Componentes\\NNICE NG249","guid":"1EO4RCWZTxmOHaDnp7PUFg","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"Abuso de alcohol","guid":"ZQHfe_iTSRWGgP7dCcGDxg","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"140","text":"Examen cardiovascular → PA acostado y de pie (OBLIGATORIO)","guid":"5lgxeFYsQf64wtgB7dWPUA","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"140","text":"Cognición y ánimo","guid":"-V82gKIoSCK85CxlapJEVw","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"140","text":"Delirium (hospital/residencia)","guid":"56vgcsyfTZi5vX-MtEKwOg","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"140","text":"Dieta, ingesta líquidos, pérdida peso","guid":"6hBXwZGSQLO25xetSK9ZCg","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"140","text":"Mareo → si vértigo rotatorio → considerar Dix-Hallpike","guid":"7XGWzRHSScKZXEveWUr3rg","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"140","text":"Calzado y condición de pies","guid":"Sr3zuqyoTNmXHK5jOanWGg","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"140","text":"Capacidad funcional percibida + preocupaciones sobre caídas","guid":"ZNifvt_FRgGnTTEuaR_qJA","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"140","text":"Marcha, balance, movilidad y fuerza muscular","guid":"55TK4AUfQCiLpHnk8A3kjg","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"140","text":"Hipoacusia","guid":"RND-UXD0S3K0qb1--uC46g","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"140","text":"Condiciones crónicas (artritis, demencia, DM, Parkinson)","guid":"rPhEagXsTEmz6VTs3D9jaA","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"140","text":"Revisión farmacológica","guid":"QgeN26nlRguMZcHu0KpYWw","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"140","text":"Examen neurológico","guid":"zYnATZseTnuXi0jovF_EGA","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"140","text":"Riesgo osteoporosis","guid":"9CQGtr-AR1WLiiuZvgF1aw","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"140","text":"Continencia urinaria","guid":"WaQcE-xiTfWW9iNz8MtFZg","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"140","text":"Déficit visual","guid":"Sj76_usiQseZbHaHDasEsQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"157","parent":"139","text":"Tests funcionales","guid":"oajMy6SCT3GmvTKG1T5Idw","children":[{"id":"158","parent":"157","text":"TUG → >12s riesgo (CDC); >10s (algunas guías); >30s riesgo mortalidad","guid":"593MBNV1RZCzEG85HafYLw","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"157","text":"Estancia unipodal → <5s patológico","guid":"vcJTi05dSmmbYW5fD-aPHw","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"157","text":"Sit to Stand 5x → >12-15s alterado","guid":"j_C7WmXpRre_vNbTP8Xi-Q","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"157","text":"SPPB → <10 puntos fragilidad y alto riesgo","guid":"MVw2pLFdS0qF53vuO8o01w","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"157","text":"Tinetti → <18 alto riesgo; 19-23 moderado; >=24 bajo","guid":"ifq4oE4IR5OFnQpJXmG-jw","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"157","text":"Test Balance 4 Estaciones → tándem <10s o 1 pie <5s → riesgo","guid":"blZyoKS8SlGSt6i_Km_ahQ","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"157","text":"Alcance funcional → <15cm alto riesgo","guid":"E0sB8CD2TB6wNaih_82R1w","children":[]}]},{"id":"165","parent":"139","text":"Dual Task → caminar + tarea cognitiva → detecta trastornos subclínicos","guid":"4lu7CracRDaw7ZmgU6w-YQ","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"139","text":"Laboratorio","guid":"nrgeC78NSH2HU3117QgGyA","children":[{"id":"167","parent":"166","text":"Hemograma, ELP, BUN/Crea, glicemia","guid":"4Rq5ZGULQ1-eBIA0efE1Gg","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"166","text":"TSH, Vitamina B12, Vitamina D","guid":"_QG0zdkdSuiKh0nNaXOlBQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"169","parent":"139","text":"Posturografía y análisis de marcha","guid":"YcbzPxMzSLKiLaTHOEUUIg","children":[{"id":"170","parent":"169","text":"Variabilidad de marcha → lo que MÁS se asocia a caídas","guid":"umkjOp0MS--rnNb2m6FH9Q","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"169","text":"Gait Plasticity → potencial biomarcador de fragilidad","guid":"zIQi8zAJQ96Wvk47t9l-7A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"172","parent":"0","text":"Intervenciones","guid":"0CA9R_qCT0-jF0b2zJNXcQ","children":[{"id":"173","parent":"172","text":"Manejo Integral Comunitario (NICE NG249)","guid":"6M97jqJqSAG0hNHWVQO7Pw","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"Abordar FR identificados en evaluación integral","guid":"ERyhfBARSra2d-gMs5VHUQ","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"173","text":"Revisión farmacológica estructurada → reducir/suspender fármacos de riesgo","guid":"o6hDzuegSn61PE6LaqCICQ","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"173","text":"Vitamina D → suplementar si déficit documentado","guid":"jei--uGGTUGEh7kwwaJVXw","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"173","text":"Ejercicio → PIEDRA ANGULAR","guid":"nxU9KanoQ8mZ34I6gBDOzQ","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"173","text":"Evaluación/intervención riesgos en hogar","guid":"LcllZlbgSvCcPqzDvTNDiw","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"173","text":"Considerar intervención quirúrgica si aplica (cataratas, podología)","guid":"HM5FTFgLQqmkl87XmpzZOw","children":[]}]},{"id":"180","parent":"172","text":"Ejercicio (Recomendación A)","guid":"I4fWwpEYRRqNtSOm6T8m0Q","children":[{"id":"181","parent":"180","text":"Reduce caídas 23% (RR 0.78 Cochrane)","guid":"QrixGhgITH2Gw6SUsJvp5Q","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"180","text":"BALANCE Y EQUILIBRIO → fundamental → tándem, Tai Chi, transferencias peso","guid":"kM4g3nh9RaWbO22Yf9RwEg","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"180","text":"Fuerza → vital en frágiles y sarcopénicos","guid":"rDebLIEDQEa2fGtJ-qZT0Q","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"180","text":"Aeróbico solo NO basta → debe asociarse a equilibrio","guid":"myC4DarrRvKoYpjwv3g6IQ","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"180","text":"Dosis efectiva → mínimo 2h/sem x 25 semanas; intensidad progresiva","guid":"PBExviEATm6Di-HJVScuAQ","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"180","text":"Tai Chi → RR 0.71 en comunidad; ROI 509%","guid":"KfquOaDcT7K4IIrkluZDsg","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"180","text":"Si alteración marcha/balance SIN otros FR → ofrecer programa ejercicio","guid":"8sc4JxaQS3CM7_w2Wi4t9A","children":[]}]},{"id":"188","parent":"172","text":"Programas con evidencia","guid":"JOnuTeNDSImdEuVr4r0qjA","children":[{"id":"189","parent":"188","text":"Otago Exercise Program → -35% caídas; ROI 127% (AM >80a frágiles)","guid":"M6tWNXl6R7q7252qRWEGmA","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"188","text":"Tai Chi Moving for Better Balance → -55% caídas; ROI 509%","guid":"s_rRUyWRSgyHmVESxVcL3w","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"188","text":"Stepping On → -30% caídas; ROI 64% (7 semanas)","guid":"yewIQfvwSMauIi9LuWjYag","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"188","text":"Marcha rápida → -52% caídas","guid":"6qWzOoFyRQaL89vEk2QmLw","children":[]}]},{"id":"193","parent":"172","text":"Intervención ambiental","guid":"8U677o2NQAeuul-i9r1kzQ","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"TO domiciliaria → reduce riesgo 21% (hasta 39% en alto riesgo)","guid":"OkIY-VksToCaFwi_jzDs9Q","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"193","text":"Discapacitados visuales → 41% reducción","guid":"Eo8260vdS5myLbb8cD3Vgg","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"193","text":"Visita aislada enfermería → NO mostró reducción","guid":"E5g2G8yIR8mEhVu6cguPtQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"197","parent":"172","text":"Oftalmología","guid":"JCTjP7UaSWSkL_TPNLU17w","children":[{"id":"198","parent":"197","text":"Cirugía cataratas 1er ojo → -34% caídas","guid":"XCn4O628Si67HrcHdM1YUA","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"197","text":"Lentes multifocales/bifocales → AUMENTAN riesgo (suelo borroso)","guid":"P1yKOVi_SZyiXZQHjC00Ag","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"197","text":"Monofocales pueden reducir caídas 40%","guid":"KPx1n_F_QtW8zT-DZtAXZA","children":[]}]},{"id":"201","parent":"172","text":"Podología","guid":"hEwgP3b7RrS-ohO3OHtzWw","children":[{"id":"202","parent":"201","text":"Puede disminuir caídas 23%","guid":"6ZW7ZELgRIuzf1Q3mQNkFg","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"201","text":"Plantillas rígidas con textura para input sensitivo","guid":"yoeOlGGjR1KBcGIuxYMLiQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"204","parent":"172","text":"Ayudas técnicas","guid":"950y6F7xQvCSCE1yFCVbnw","children":[{"id":"205","parent":"204","text":"Bastones/andadores → beneficio movilidad pero SIN claro beneficio prevención","guid":"78EbEP0eTSGcdrNlg1Yx2A","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"204","text":"Protectores cadera → RR 0.82 institucionalizados → baja adherencia","guid":"WfWIRZHLQ02chbtrqFfX8Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"207","parent":"172","text":"Residencias y hospitales","guid":"wmELMSOoTL-CjuvVIJ0UHw","children":[{"id":"208","parent":"207","text":"Evaluación integral automática al ingreso","guid":"pVJvK9A_QbebLn1heS2woA","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"207","text":"Abordar FR identificados","guid":"JagxlVzNS2eOeUazPpI3Cg","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"207","text":"Revisión farmacológica","guid":"CblePAnZSvSilgbN0su9QQ","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"207","text":"Vitamina D si déficit","guid":"L6iSx53cTmi4_blzE2d1Vg","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"207","text":"Ejercicio adaptado","guid":"O3xPZHhLShaK0t1-la_20Q","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"207","text":"Intervención ambiental","guid":"yg7iEZbBQvmPpd1ohglbzw","children":[]}]},{"id":"214","parent":"172","text":"Algoritmo STEADI (CDC)","guid":"1M4nogjFQdWeje74dgY7Zg","children":[{"id":"215","parent":"214","text":"Screen → Stay Independent >=4, caída con lesión, >=2 caídas","guid":"usLgHeJTSDCyV5aiGfkFxQ","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"214","text":"Assess → TUG, 30s Chair Stand, 4-Stage Balance, HO","guid":"S-4Mfi4nTdiWNgOtavvjnw","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"214","text":"Intervene → Vit D, revisión meds, Kine/TO, comorbilidades","guid":"SpPMgIO_Rdak5kcchbARJg","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"214","text":"Follow-up → 30-90 días","guid":"tzRw6TekQdeq3TUbVMUsgA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"219","parent":"0","text":"Maximizar Adherencia (NICE NG249)","guid":"8HKtT2YKSvyUlKnuyWPIgw","children":[{"id":"220","parent":"219","text":"Adaptar intervención a preferencias y capacidades","guid":"KIHYUCoyQ7KDTP4Imfq67A","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"219","text":"Considerar barreras (transporte, motivación, dolor)","guid":"CLLOtYLgSEC2Xyded2FuhA","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"219","text":"NICE → TCC si miedo a caer no mejora con ejercicio","guid":"4DEbHvRGQSyODINhzt1TVg","children":[]},{"id":"223","parent":"219","text":"Educación → informar sobre riesgo, beneficios de ejercicio, modificaciones hogar","guid":"n77X9TugSsqCqvmh83SuAw","children":[]}]},{"id":"224","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clínicas","guid":"BnHeCvJURLiUR6w0tGnXeA","children":[{"id":"225","parent":"224","text":"Caída en último año = automáticamente en riesgo → predictor más simple y potente","guid":"G1DSy7b8Q4C7XQdVvQ3AFg","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"224","text":"Caída en casa = frágil/enfermo vs caída en calle = activo/vigoroso","guid":"iexjogOxTbqAlgV3scuV0Q","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"224","text":"Mayor riesgo farmacológico → primeras 24h de inicio/ajuste","guid":"wfiHqaihQTaa9fI3Z4JVhA","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"224","text":"Lentes multifocales distorsionan suelo → cambiar a monofocales (-40% caídas)","guid":"l1TsnLdqSSe4J9Vkl6d5NA","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"224","text":"ANTICOAGULACIÓN → riesgo ACV sin ACO supera 10x el riesgo sangrado por caída → NO contraindicar ACO solo por riesgo caídas","guid":"EJp7Yp5IRhyi3LQxAewhQA","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"224","text":"Mareo postural sin baja PA en cifras → manejar como ortostatismo","guid":"lYhUItYDS7Gzla7cAz8_dA","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"224","text":"Dolor → a mayor intensidad y sitios con dolor, mayor riesgo caída","guid":"dRlB34SRT8aUVU7a6g2ekA","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"224","text":"Post-alta hospitalaria → riesgo paradójico aumentado (hasta 43%) por recuperación movilidad sin fuerza/balance","guid":"i7qd0qICRdikcAxIjfVOlw","children":[]},{"id":"233","parent":"224","text":"Deterioro cognitivo no amnésico (frontal) → más caídas que Alzheimer típico","guid":"AI89z5R2QCajSlfEKZDN3Q","children":[]},{"id":"234","parent":"224","text":"NICE 2025 amplía cobertura a 50-64a con FR (demencia, Parkinson, discapacidad intelectual)","guid":"48FHoIQySwWWpqSw8IDGuA","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"224","text":"NO usar herramientas predictivas de riesgo → NICE 2025 explícito","guid":"TEjfKgP2S0u3tULsMUYsTg","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"224","text":"Variabilidad de marcha → mejor predictor que velocidad aislada","guid":"jwiPPiwrTx6G7yIwlFelPg","children":[]},{"id":"237","parent":"224","text":"TUG >10-12s → punto de corte clave para iniciar intervención","guid":"RRjCWX56Q6KZ1BzGlPQLCQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"238","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"2o284khlTV2ZKeMVhQiNBQ","children":[{"id":"239","parent":"238","text":"1. NICE. Falls: assessment and prevention in older people and in people 50 and over at higher risk. NG249. London: NICE; 2025.","guid":"k7jSe1IWRc-iaYJoHo_ZEw","children":[]},{"id":"240","parent":"238","text":"2. Montero-Odasso M et al. World guidelines for falls prevention and management. Age Ageing. 2022;51(9):afac205.","guid":"_WE6LSX6R3-X6lPnrlxT3w","children":[]},{"id":"241","parent":"238","text":"3. Gillespie LD et al. Interventions for preventing falls in older people. Cochrane Database Syst Rev. 2012;(9):CD007146.","guid":"Dfr62Y-jRwKFGeHsIobG5Q","children":[]},{"id":"242","parent":"238","text":"4. Tinetti ME et al. Risk factors for falls among elderly persons living in the community. N Engl J Med. 1988;319(26):1701-7.","guid":"p4rpIPnCT9yPCX73GRq7OQ","children":[]},{"id":"243","parent":"238","text":"5. Panel on Prevention of Falls in Older Persons, AGS/BGS. Summary of updated AGS/BGS clinical practice guideline. J Am Geriatr Soc. 2011;59(1):148-57.","guid":"kOEFfjsATuWQ0BdOAJSApQ","children":[]},{"id":"244","parent":"238","text":"6. BMJ Visual Summary. Falls in older people: Assessment and prevention. BMJ. 2026.","guid":"4FSg6_RlRiu5Feef1ziqxQ","children":[]},{"id":"245","parent":"238","text":"7. Rubenstein LZ. Falls in older people: epidemiology, risk factors and strategies for prevention. Age Ageing. 2006;35(Suppl 2):ii37-ii41.","guid":"nSltbt-iR36DcEFxd0iGKQ","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":245,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Geriatría","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Geriatría","filename":"Caidas Adulto Mayor NICE2025-1","id":"map_914","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Caidas Adulto Mayor NICE2025-1"}